    <h2 class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-6">When to use the NHS number pattern</h2>
    <p>Follow this pattern whenever you need to ask for an NHS number.</p>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="nhsuk-grid-row">
  <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-two-thirds">

    <h2 class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-6">When not to use the NHS number pattern</h2>
    <p>Only ask for an NHS number if your service needs it or if the user is more likely to succeed on their journey if they can provide it.</p>
    <p>Users do not need to know their NHS number to receive care. This means that the NHS number is not a well-known identifier.</p>
    
  </div>
</div>




