  Your NHS number is a 10 digit number that you find on any letter sent to you by the NHS. For example, 458 777 3456
</span>

    <span class="nhsuk-error-message">
    <span class="nhsuk-u-visually-hidden">Error:</span> Your NHS number is too long
    </span>

    <div class="nhsuk-form-group">
  <input class="nhsuk-input nhsuk-input--width-10" id="input-width-10" name="test-width-10" type="text">
</div>
  </fieldset>

</div>
              
          </div>
        
